Package ohos.event.intentagent

Interface IntentAgent.OnCompleted

  • Enclosing class:
    IntentAgent

    public static interface IntentAgent.OnCompleted
    A callback for the IntentAgentHelper#triggerIntentAgent(Context, IntentAgent, IntentAgent.OnCompleted, EventHandler, TriggerInfo) method. After the method execution is complete, the callback process will start.
    Since:
    3

      • onSendCompleted

        void onSendCompleted​(IntentAgent intentAgent,
                     Intent intent,
                     int finalCode,
                     String finalData,
                     IntentParams extraInfo)
        Called when execution of the IntentAgentHelper#triggerIntentAgent(Context, IntentAgent, IntentAgent.OnCompleted, EventHandler, TriggerInfo) method is complete.
        Parameters:
        intentAgent - Indicates the triggered IntentAgent.
        intent - Indicates the existing intent that is triggered.
        finalCode - Indicates the request code used to trigger the IntentAgent.
        finalData - Indicates the final data collected by the common events.
        extraInfo - Indicates the final extra information collected by the common events.
